u can find it at Indian or Asian food stores.","You can find tinned jackfruit in brine at some major supermarkets in the international aisle or in Asian food stores. Be sure to purchase the fruit in brine (it's also sold tinned in syrup).","You can serve this filling in sandwiches, in wraps or pitas, as a topping for baked potatoes or as a dip with crudités.","You can store this filling in the refrigerator for up to 3 days."],"basicInfo":["easy","5m","5m","4 portions"]}